  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a medium bowl, whisk the flour, cocoa powder, granulated sugar, baking powder, salt, vanilla, egg, and oil until smooth. </step>
    <step num="1">Add the chocolate cake batter to a mini frying pan over low heat, and spread to smooth the top. </step>
    <step num="2">Cover with a small plate and cook for 30 minutes, or until the cake is set. </step>
    <step num="3">Serve with powdered sugar and berries (optional). </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
